One person has died while six others have been injured in a road crash at Total trading centre in Mau Summit, along the Nakuru-Eldoret highway.
Mau Summit Base Commander James Ademba said the on Thursday evening crash occurred when the driver of a 14-seater matatu that was heading to Eldoret from Nakuru lost control of the vehicle and veered off the road.



